
configuring dubug.
-------------------
-Xdebug -Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=8787  = Add this line into setenv in bin folder.

LDS -> Run -> Debug Configuration -> Remote Java Application -> chnage port -& add class> apply

increasing gradle size.
-------------------
org.gradle.daemon=true
org.gradle.jvmargs=-Xmx2560m
 add into gradle.properties file.
